## Attribution

This research project builds upon the Quorum Dev Quickstart by ConsenSys,
extending it with custom smart contracts and performance benchmarking tools
for comparing consensus algorithms (IBFT, QBFT, Raft).

Original work by ConsenSys Software Inc. is licensed under Apache-2.0.
Our modifications and additions are licensed under MIT.
